numbakit-ode Changelog
======================

0.6 (unreleased)
----------------

- Nothing changed yet.


0.5 (2022-04-06)
----------------

- Implemented events.
- Implemented interpolator for RungeKutta23, RungeKutta45, DOP853.
- Added NO_NUMBA variable to nbcompat.
- Implemented bounded bisect method for root finding.
- Several bug fixed and code clean up.
- Improvements to the documentation, packaging and testing infrastructure.


0.4 (2020-12-27)
----------------

- Moved t_bound check to Solver class.
- Created ALIAS API to allow multiple names for solvers while keeping
  a preferred one.
- Changed import system in module..
- Reorganized solvers into multistep and rungekutta.


0.3 (2020-11-15)
----------------

- Improved public API: skip / step / run


0.2 (2020-11-08)
----------------

- Tidy up part of the public API.
- Renamed some variables in internal methods for consistency.
- Improved docstrings.
- API to handle the first step in higher order fixed step methods.


0.1 (2020-11-05)
----------------

- First public release.
